    "This is the most important cell in this section. Run the same query with\n",
    "the weakest and strongest prompt and compare the results side by side.\n",
    "\n",
    "**What to watch for:**\n",
    "- Does V1 use the tools, or answer from training data?\n",
    "- Does V1's output parse successfully?\n",
    "- Is the V4 severity field always present and consistently formatted?\n",
    "- Does V4 still hallucinate, or does the constraint stop it?"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
