   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "part9-summary",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Part 9 Summary\n",
    "\n",
    "| Technique | One-line summary | Impact |\n",
    "|---|---|---|\n",
    "| Output Format Enforcement | Tell the agent the exact format, not just the task | Eliminates most `OutputParserException` errors |\n",
    "| Role + Constraint Framing | Give a job description, not a job title | Reduces hallucination and off-topic responses |\n",
    "| Few-Shot Examples | Show a complete, correct example before the query | Highest reliability, small token cost |\n",
    "| Structured Output Parsing | Parse Final Answer into a Python object | Makes output usable by downstream systems |\n",
    "| Prompt Versioning | Track prompt changes like code changes | Lets you diagnose reliability regressions |\n",
    "\n",
    "**The rule of thumb:** Before blaming the model, check the prompt.\n",
    "Most agent failures are prompt failures."
   ]
  }
 ]
